#begin start
{{ hour = game_hour }}
{{ if hour < 9 || hour >= 20 }}
The clothing store is shuttered. The window display is lit — a few mannequins in this season's looks — but the door is locked.
<p style="color:#888; font-size:11px">Open 09:00 – 20:00.</p>
[[City Centre, city_center]]
{{ else }}
You push open the glass door and step into the clothing store. Soft music plays. Racks of folded and hanging clothes fill the space in neat, colour-coded rows.
<p>A shop assistant glances up from behind the counter and gives a brief, professional smile. You're free to browse.</p>
{{ kron = item_count "kron" }}
<p>You have <strong>{{ kron }} Kron</strong>.</p>

<p style="color:#888; font-size:11px; font-style:italic">— Activewear —</p>
{{ has_sport = has_clothing "sport_outfit" }}
{{ if has_sport }}
<p><strong>Sport Set</strong> — leggings and crop top, 45 Kron <span style="color:#4CAF50; font-size:11px">✓</span></p>
{{ else if kron >= 45 }}
<p><strong>Sport Set</strong> — stretchy leggings and a fitted crop top. Good for working out or just looking like you might. 45 Kron. <a href="acvn://city_clothingstore/buysportoutfit">→ Buy</a></p>
{{ else }}
<p><strong>Sport Set</strong> — leggings and crop top, 45 Kron <span style="color:#888; font-size:11px">not enough funds</span></p>
