#begin buysportoutfit
You pull the set from the rack in your size and try it on in the fitting room. The leggings are high-waisted and comfortable. The crop top fits well.
<p>You bring it to the counter. The assistant folds it efficiently into a paper bag.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 45 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "sport_outfit" }}
{{ has_shoes = has_clothing "sport_shoes" }}
{{ if has_shoes }}
{{ if (quest_step "get_active") == 0 }}{{ advance_quest "get_active" }}{{ end }}
<p><em>You now have everything you need to get moving.</em></p>
{{ else }}
<p><em>Sport Set added to your wardrobe. Pick up some sport shoes to complete the look.</em></p>
{{ end }}
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buyyogaset
You take the set from the rack and slip into the fitting room. The fabric is soft but structured — it holds without digging in.
<p>You check yourself in the mirror for a moment longer than strictly necessary. You buy it.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 40 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "yoga_set" }}
<p><em>Yoga Set added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buyrunningshorts
The shorts are lighter than they look. The tank top is airy enough that you almost don't notice it.
<p>You fold them over your arm and bring them to the till.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 28 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "running_shorts" }}
<p><em>Running Shorts & Tank added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buysportshoes
