#end

#begin buysundress
You hold it up, then try it on. The fabric is light. The fit is good without trying.
<p>You buy it without much deliberation.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 38 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "sundress" }}
<p><em>Summer Dress added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buyjeanblouse
You take both pieces into the fitting room. The jeans are firm but they give a little. The blouse tucks in loosely.
<p>The whole thing works. You bring it to the counter.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 48 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "jeans_blouse" }}
<p><em>Slim Jeans & Blouse added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buyminiskirt
You try it on. The skirt sits high and ends short — it asks you to stand up straight. The top fits close.
<p>You look at yourself in the fitting room mirror for a moment. Then you bring it to the till.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 42 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "miniskirt_top" }}
<p><em>Mini Skirt & Top added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buypartyoutfit
It's the kind of outfit that asks something of you — a little more confidence, a little more presence. You try it on. It delivers.
<p>You bring it to the counter without hesitating.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 55 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "party_outfit" }}
<p><em>Night Out Outfit added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buyeveningdress
The dress is heavier than it looks. It falls properly — the kind of weight that moves well.
<p>You stand in the fitting room and look at yourself in it for a while. It's the kind of thing that changes how you hold yourself.</p>
<p>You bring it to the counter.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 90 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "evening_dress" }}
<p><em>Evening Dress added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
#end

#begin buylacebra
The bralette is in a small hanger — barely anything to it. The lace is fine and soft against the back of your hand.
<p>You try it on. It fits delicately. You buy it.</p>
{{ spend_item "kron" 28 }}
{{ unlock_clothing "bra_lace" }}
<p><em>Lace Bralette added to your wardrobe.</em></p>
[[Clothing Store, city_clothingstore]]
[[Leave, city_center]]
